Title: Stonewall
Feature: Creates a wall of stone that blocks incoming projectiles.

Title: Rock Shield
Feature: Creates a barrier of stone that reduces damage taken.

Title: Mudslide
Feature: Creates a mudslide that slows down and damages enemies.

Title: Stone Fist
Feature: Deals earth damage with a powerful punch that stuns the target.

Title: Earthquake
Feature: Shakes the ground, dealing damage and stunning enemies.
